# Implementation Plan: Replace Sequence Run Detection with Mark Played on Start

Replace the legacy "Sequence Run Detection" setting (chronological next-show prediction) with a new feature that marks a show as played immediately upon starting the first track, rather than waiting for a show transition or completion.

## Proposed Changes

### [Component] shakedown_core (Settings & Logic)

#### [MODIFY] [default_settings.dart](file:///c:/Users/jeff/StudioProjects/gdar/packages/shakedown_core/lib/config/default_settings.dart)
- Replace `enableRunDetection` with `markPlayedOnStart` (default: `false`).

#### [MODIFY] [settings_provider_core.dart](file:///c:/Users/jeff/StudioProjects/gdar/packages/shakedown_core/lib/providers/settings_provider_core.dart)
- Rename `_enableRunDetectionKey` constant to `_markPlayedOnStartKey`.
- Rename `_enableRunDetection` field to `_markPlayedOnStart`.
- Update getter `enableRunDetection` to `markPlayedOnStart`.
- Rename [toggleEnableRunDetection](file:///c:/Users/jeff/StudioProjects/gdar/packages/shakedown_core/lib/providers/settings_provider_core.dart#264-268) to `toggleMarkPlayedOnStart`.

#### [MODIFY] [settings_provider_initialization.dart](file:///c:/Users/jeff/StudioProjects/gdar/packages/shakedown_core/lib/providers/settings_provider_initialization.dart)
- Update code to load/initialize `_markPlayedOnStart` from preference key.

#### [MODIFY] [random_show_selector.dart](file:///c:/Users/jeff/StudioProjects/gdar/packages/shakedown_core/lib/services/random_show_selector.dart)
- Remove [_suggestFromRun](file:///c:/Users/jeff/StudioProjects/gdar/packages/shakedown_core/lib/services/random_show_selector.dart#233-269) logic and references to `enableRunDetection`.
- Chronological prediction is being retired as part of this setting replacement.

#### [MODIFY] [audio_provider_playback.dart](file:///c:/Users/jeff/StudioProjects/gdar/packages/shakedown_core/lib/providers/audio_provider_playback.dart)
- Update [playSource](file:///c:/Users/jeff/StudioProjects/gdar/packages/shakedown_core/lib/providers/audio_provider_playback.dart#105-140) to check `settingsProvider.markPlayedOnStart`.
- If true, call `catalogService.markAsPlayed()` and [incrementPlayCount()](file:///c:/Users/jeff/StudioProjects/gdar/packages/shakedown_core/lib/services/catalog_service.dart#219-228) immediately.
- Set `_hasMarkedAsPlayed = true` to prevent redundant marking during the session.

