### Manual Verification
1. Open **Settings -> Playback**.
2. Verify "Sequence Run Detection" is replaced by **Mark Played on Start**.
3. Toggle it **ON**.
4. Play an unplayed show and verify it is marked "Played" in the UI/catalog immediately.
5. Toggle it **OFF** and verify "Played" status is deferred (current behavior).
